Look at how this paragraph looks in the Edit Window.
It has broken down into several lines but are still displayed together.

Type something in Edit mode and see how it is displayed using the '''Show preview''' button.
You can make some change, click ''Show preview''.
Then make some more change, click ''Show preview'' again.
How the Preview is displaying is controlled by what is in the current Edit Window.

Click on '''Cancel''' when you are done.

Use the ''back'' button '''on your browser''' to go back to the previous Wiki page.
You have to click the ''back'' button many times to '''pass through all your preview pages''' before you come back to the tutorial.
